divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home. Saw it in sky, watched it, about 20 seconds it moved then disappears distant in the sky. Pretty far. Thought it was a bright satellite. Very sharp pain in the head after disappearing. never get headaches normally. Thought it was weird, looked up other ufo events today found a few outside pewaukee.
